# Reward Program Agent

An AI-powered Reward Program Investigation Assistant that uses an LLM to intelligently select business tools, investigate reward program data, and generate natural language responses.

This project demonstrates how Large Language Models can orchestrate business logic through tool calling rather than relying only on Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).

Here is the github link

https://github.com/shankambur/reward-program-agent

---

## Features

- AI-powered tool selection
- Customer investigation
- Offer investigation
- Submission investigation
- Business service layer
- Repository pattern
- Natural language response generation
- Streamlit web interface

---

